{"tid":1960702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"親共議員冀推遲立法會選舉, 聶德權 : 密切留意","createTime":"2020-04-06T10:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T10:46:06.000Z","uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"52a8b26f6d5e3a6c8da2b7e5565470a20afdb7a0","tid":1960702,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:11:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518824-20200404.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518824-20200404.htm&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=ed238fe0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518824-20200404.htm&h=ec100cd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518824-20200404.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n 建制派冀推遲立會選舉 聶德權稱密切留意按疫情評估<br />\n2020-04-04 HKT 10:15<br />\n<br />\n對於有建制派議員建議推遲9月舉行的立法會選舉，政制及內地事務局局長聶德權表示，目前面對疫情，當局會密切注意情況，以作評估及安排，但現時很清楚的是，當局會做好有關選舉的工作，包括選民登記等。<br />\n<br />\n至於籌備進度會否受影響，聶德權說當局會盡力處理，目前在疫情影響下，不同部門的工作或多或少都受影響，當局作出各種應變和準備。"},{"pid":"4814049bbe24df7d1ddfca480ab0ba8e39c44b9a","tid":1960702,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:12:30.000Z","msg":"李慧琼：對9月能夠維持公平立法會選舉沒有信心！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1960544/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1960544/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"6cbf96b00f15067083fd7e1cbf49849647f6187e","tid":1960702,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78676e0da4ff2c26e7ceb505d238f0d059ccbefc","tid":1960702,"uid":33174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:15:59.000Z","msg":"正喎 不如推遲埋特首選舉 永續林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b14e7faaf15048ee7e52ef27e40f2fcc3c5c8e6","tid":1960702,